			A goal of Alpacas at Lone Ranch is for you to become loyal customers who will avail themselves of our special animals and services.<br>
			<br>

			<b>The End-Of-The-Year Private Sale</b><br>
			This unadvertised private sale, held at the end of each year, is open exclusively to prior alpaca purchasers.  It features fine Alpacas at significantly reduced (40% to 60% off) prices.  These are the same high quality Alpacas offered at established advertised prices all year, but happen not to have sold.  They come with the usual services and guarantees.  This is a special opportunity to build a herd and accelerate value.  We do this in an effort to develop loyal relationships with a select group of customers.<br>
			<br>

			<b>Sales Brokering Program</b><br>
			Any animal purchased from Alpacas at Lone Ranch, including its offspring, may be added to our distributed sales list and website on the Internet.  This is free of charge including any associated advertising.  If one of your alpacas sells as a result of our brokerage efforts,  our fee is 10% of the sales price.  This is a quick and easy way for you to begin offering animals up for sale. 
		
